-- Weber Supports Mayrhuber as Lufthansa Chairman, Boersen Reports
-- B y   O l i v e r   S u e s s
-- 2012-04-30T16:36:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-30/weber-supports-mayrhuber-as-lufthansa-chairman-boersen-reports.html
Juergen Weber, chairman of  Deutsche
Lufthansa AG (LHA) ’s supervisory board, supports  Wolfgang Mayrhuber ,
the airline’s former chief executive officer, as a candidate to
succeed him next year,  Boersen-Zeitung  reported, citing an
interview with Weber.  To contact the reporter on this story:
